instructions: Place dinner plate on table cloth
Place salad plate on top of the dinner plate
Place napkin on top of the salad plate
Place wine glass on the upper right corner of the table cloth
Place water glass right next to the wine glass in a lower right diagonal direction
Place salad fork on the table cloth next to the dinner plate
Place the dinner fork next to the salad fork on top of the table cloth
Place the dinner knife on the right side of the dinner plate
Place  the soup spoon next to the dinner knife on top of the table cloth
